sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as ODH Model Controller<br/>Webhook 443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant IstioGW as Istio Gateway<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>5001/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP HTTP
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: Submit InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: OIDC/Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate InferenceService<br/>mTLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allow (mutated)
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route, VirtualService<br/>AuthConfig, ServiceMonitor<br/>NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>MR: Register InferenceService metadata<br/>Auth: TLS
        KServe->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>or K8s Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over User,NGC: Flow 2: NIM Account Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR<br/>with NGC API key<br/>Auth: OIDC/Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate Account spec<br/>mTLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allow
        Controller->>NGC: Validate account<br/>Fetch model list<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
        NGC-->>Controller: Model catalog
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (models)<br/>Secret (pull secret)<br/>Template (ServingRuntime)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Inference Request (Serverless + Service Mesh)
        User->>Route: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        Route->>IstioGW: Forward to ingress
        IstioGW->>Authorino: Validate JWT (if AuthConfig enabled)<br/>gRPC mTLS
        Authorino-->>IstioGW: Auth OK
        IstioGW->>Activator: Route to activator<br/>(if scaled to zero)
        Activator->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>mTLS (if PeerAuth enabled)
        Predictor->>S3: Load model artifacts<br/>Auth: IAM/Access Key
        S3-->>Predictor: Model data
        Predictor-->>Activator: Prediction result
        Activator-->>IstioGW: Response
        IstioGW-->>Route: Response
        Route-->>User: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 245)
        Note over Prometheus,MR: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
        Prometheus->>Predictor: Scrape inference metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>mTLS (if configured)
        Predictor-->>Prometheus: Model metrics
    end
